    • clickCoursesLink

      @When("the user clicks the {string} link in the menu section") public void clickCoursesLink(String linkText)
      Implementation for the step 'When the user clicks the {string} link in the menu section' Only implemented for String = 'Courses'
      Parameters:
      linkText - The text in homepage menu that one wants to press.

    • verifyCoursesPage

      @Then("the user should see a page with all the courses listed") public void verifyCoursesPage()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user should see a page with all the courses listed'. Checks if there are any courses listed at all. Gives assertion if there are no courses listed.

    • verifyCourseAndProfessorNames

      @Then("for each course, there should be a page that is loaded and there should be a professor") public void verifyCourseAndProfessorNames()
      Implementation for the step 'Then for each course, there should be a page that is loaded and there should be a professor' Clicks link of all the courses on the Course pages. Give assertion if for one of these courses, the details page doesn't load. Checks on that detailed page if there are any professors specified. Gives assertion if for one of these courses, there is no professor specified. Prints professor(s) of each course.

    • navigateToSoftwareTestingPage

      @Given("the user is on the Software Testing course page") public void navigateToSoftwareTestingPage()
      Implementation for the step 'The user is on the Software Testing course page.'

    • areThereAssignmentsLinksPresent

      @When("the user sees the links for each assignment") public void areThereAssignmentsLinksPresent()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user sees the links for each assignment'. Checks if there are any assignments links listed at all. Gives assertion if there are no assignments listed.

    • verifyAssignmentsLinkFormat

      @Then("the user should verify the link format of each assignment link") public void verifyAssignmentsLinkFormat()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user should verify the link format of each assignment link'. For each assignment listed, checks that the link is of the format '/system/files/uploads/courses/Testing/assignment[NR].pdf' Gives assertion if the layout differs for one of the assignments.

    • verifyAssignmentsLinkExistence

      @Then("the user should verify the document existence of each assignment link") public void verifyAssignmentsLinkExistence()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user should verify the document existence of each assignment link'. For each assignment listed, verify that the document (link) exists on the server. Gives a warning when it does not exist.

    • userInput

      @When("the user says that a student {} belongs to student group {}") public void userInput(String name, String group)
      Implementation for the step 'When the user says that a student {} belongs to student group'.
      Parameters:
      name - Full Name with capital letters like one should from the student.
      group - Number of One (of the) student group(s) the student believes he is in.

    • theUserShouldBeInAStudentGroup

      @Then("the user should be in a student group") public void theUserShouldBeInAStudentGroup()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user should be in a student group'. Gives an assertion when the student cannot be found in any group.

    • theUserIsInThatStudentGroup

      @And("the user should receive a warning when he does not belong to that student group number") public void theUserIsInThatStudentGroup()
      Implementation for the step 'And the user should receive a warning when he does not belong to that student group number.'

    • PresenceAsPresenter

      @Then("the user should see his mandatory presence as presenter") public void PresenceAsPresenter()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user should see his mandatory presence as presenter'. Prints the date that the student needs to present a lecture.

    • PresenceAsOpponent

      @And("the user should see his mandatory presence as opponent") public void PresenceAsOpponent()
      Implementation for the step 'Then the user should see his mandatory presence as opponent'. Prints the date that the student is an opponent.
